<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Jimmy Santiago Baca</span></strong> spent five years in prison in Arizona and is now writing in the country in Hurdle Mills, N.C.</p><a href="/contributors/jimmy-santiago-baca" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
